    "reference_confidence": 0.95
  },
  "reconstructed_intent": "用户希望查看上季度购买重疾险的客户画像，属于 customer_portrait 意图",
  "judge_basis": "对比实际输出（intent=other, confidence=0.5, target_value=null）与业务预期（intent=customer_portrait, target_value=重疾险）",
